body:
What If Game

So, my friends and I like playing the “what if” game or “what would you do in this scenario game” and they’re like. So, Al, what would you do if you met Tom Holland.


Well friends, as much as I’d like to say I’d be confident enough to grab a picture with him or at least say hello. I would probably panic because I didn’t look cute enough and hide. Without a doubt. THEREFORE. Happy that particular scenario is not likely. I’d spontaneously combust.


“AL ITS TOM HOLLAND”


BOOM. DEAD. GONE. POINT OF NO RETURN.

tags: another episode on Peter Parker is me
body:
Peter Parker Slime Headcanon!

-ok so Peter, having his senses dialed up to 11 on a good day, just fucking loves slime

-the way it feels? Amazing. The way it sounds? Great. Just slime in general? 10/10 he loves it so much

-in fact he even makes his own slime (of course he does)

-it was actually the starting point for his web solution ideas

-he tried selling it as Peter Parker but no one really wanted to buy it

-Tony found out abt slime through some news article and asks Peter bc “it seems like something you’d like”

-to no ones surprise Peter pulls out like 20 little jars of all sorts of different slimes and starts explaining each one to Tony

-Tony of course thinks it’s adorable and so he makes some out of like the best ingredients and it can do all sorts of new and improved slime (because it’s all really just chemistry)

-Peter is enthralled by this, and obviously wants to share it with everyone else so he makes Tony Stark of all people get an Etsy and they sell avengers themed slimes as well as give out the recipes just in case someone wants to make it on their own

-bonus points if no one realizes that the Etsy seller is actually Tony Stark
